Title: Campaigning Religions
---
As the intelligence of the human race evolves all the competing -- campaigning
  as it were -- religions will be viewed differently.

One will see they are all basically contestants in a beauty pageant,

and the religion that can make your own beauty most known will win your most
  respect.
